<h2>Hello <%= @resource.first_name %>!</h2>

<p>Someone has requested to reset your password for the LECOM Ladder website.</p>

<p><strong>If you don't know anything about this, simply ignore this email. Nothing will change.</strong></p>

<p>Otherwise, click the button below and it will take you through the process of getting a new password.</p>

<p>
	<%= link_to edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @token), class: "btn" do %>
		&gt;&gt; Change my password
	<% end %>
</p>

<br>

<table class="callout" cellpadding="15">
	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#ECF8FF">
			<p><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong><br>Your password won't change until you click the button above and create a new one.</p>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>